channel.title: I KNOW that this is a VERY nooby question but:
channel.description:
Ok... I have noticed that i had like 4 JDK 6s installed (don't ask me why) so i uninstall them and go to www.sun.com and see that the Java 6 update 1 is no longer there, it's replaced with update 2. So i install update 2 and try to compile me server and it says the stupid you don't have jdk 5 or 6 etc... So i'm like WTF i do have JDK 6 but I'm wondering if i need JRE also because that's what i also had... Please help me out rofl... I've never solved this problem before because i never uninstalled my Java...
Thank you, -Zaron
